<%= render "shared/flash_messages" %>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center m-10">
  <%= image_tag "SweetsLog_logo.png" %>
  <ul class= "text-center text-xs sm:text-base text-yellow-900">
    <li>美味しい<span class="font-bold text-base sm:text-lg">「スイーツ」</span>を食べた</li>
    <li>幸せな思い出<span class="font-bold text-base sm:text-lg">「ログ」</span>しよう</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="overflow-hidden">
  <div class="slider">
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <% if post.image.attached? %>
        <div><%= image_tag(post.image.variant(resize_to_fill: [320, 320]), class:"rounded-xl") %></div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center animate-bounce">
  <span class="mt-5 text-yellow-900">Scroll</span>
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-5 text-yellow-900">
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.47 13.28a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 0l7.5-7.5a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06L12 11.69 5.03 4.72a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06l7.5 7.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.47 19.28a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 0l7.5-7.5a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06-1.06L12 17.69l-6.97-6.97a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06l7.5 7.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
  </svg>
</div>

<div class="box fadeIn">
  <div class="m-10 text-center text-xs sm:text-base text-yellow-900">
    <ul>
      <li><span class="text-lg font-bold">SweetsLog</span> は</li>
      <li>美味しいスイーツを食べた幸せな記憶を記録し、</li>
      <li>シェアできるアプリです。</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[90%]">
    <div class="mb-12 justify-items-center grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="w-75 h-75 p-10 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl">
        <div class= "flex flex-wrap justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "top_posts_icon.png" %>
          <div class="pt-4 text-center text-yellow-900">
            <ul>
              <li>美味しいスイーツを食べた</li>
              <li>幸せな気持ちを写真や</li>
              <li>店舗名と共に投稿。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-75 h-75 p-10 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl">
        <div class= "flex flex-wrap justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "top_likes_icon.png" %>
          <div class="pt-4 text-center text-yellow-900">
            <ul>
              <li>みんなの投稿を見て、</li>
              <li>食べてみたいスイーツを</li>
              <li>お気に入り登録。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-75 h-75 p-10 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl">
        <div class= "flex flex-wrap justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "top_search_icon.png" %>
          <div class="text-center text-yellow-900 mt-4">
            <ul>
              <li>都道府県・メニュー名・</li>
              <li>キーワード等の項目で</li>
              <li>投稿を検索できます。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-75 h-75 p-10 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl">
        <div class= "flex flex-wrap justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "top_diagnoses_icon.png" %>
          <div class="pt-4 text-center text-yellow-900">
            <ul>
              <li>何を食べるか迷ったときは、</li>
              <li>スイーツ診断。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-[90%] text-white md:w-90 mx-auto mb-12 text-center text-base">
      <%= link_to 'みんなの投稿を見る', posts_path, class: "block px-5 py-2.5 bg-yellow-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-yellow-700" %>
      <% unless user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to '会員登録（無料）をして使ってみる', new_user_registration_path, class: "mt-4 block px-5 py-2.5 bg-yellow-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-yellow-700" %>
      <% end %>
   </div>
  </div>
</div>